      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/banco-bpm-board-member-says-unicredit-bid-is-hostile-ansa-reports-2024-11-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利联合信贷银行（UniCredit）的一名董事会成员周二向意大利安莎通讯社表示，该银行对意大利 BPM 银行的意外收购是恶意的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/banco-bpm-board-member-says-unicredit-bid-is-hostile-ansa-reports-2024-11-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 08:37:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲复兴开发银行称全球保护性工业政策复苏</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/global-resurgence-protective-industrial-policies-ebrd-says-2024-11-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲复兴开发银行在一份年度报告中指出，旨在促进或保护国内利益的产业政策在全球范围内复苏，威胁到国际合作，并可能特别损害较贫穷的国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/global-resurgence-protective-industrial-policies-ebrd-says-2024-11-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 06:13:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
